<s> Currently, you can specify a "Depth:infinity" header for MERGE.  </s>
<s> Since you can get the same effect by saying that a MERGE is always depth infinity, and that you can just use the version URL of a version-controlled collection if you want a "Depth:0" merge, I vote that we remove the Depth header as a needless complication to the MERGE method.  </s>
<s> Any objections?  </s>
<s> Cheers, Geoff  </s>
